data.description: Beautiful home built in the last year just steps from the local shops & restaurants of Downtown Lancaster. Welcome home! Enjoy all seasons with your huge covered front porch and walk into the open living plan main level. Vinyl plank flooring throughout first floor as you flow from large living room into the gorgeous bright kitchen. White cabinets with light granite counters and SS appliances plus island/breakfast bar for additional seating and a full pantry for storage. Formal dining area off to the side with door leading to back deck ideal for grilling and enjoying cool evenings. Upstairs find the primary bedroom suite with attached bath. The bright updated feeling from the kitchen continues with both full bathrooms upstairs. 2 additional bedrooms idea for family, guests, or a home office space!  Location of home couldn't be better - convenient to EVERYTHING including access to the interstate for any possible commutes to Charlotte or Columbia. A MUST SEE!
